OL,3,CTickets for 99th Royal Variety
OL,4,CPerformance go on sale this Friday
OL,6,FTickets for the 99th Royal Variety
OL,7,FPerformance are to go on sale on
OL,8,FFriday, with the annual show set for
OL,9,Fthe Royal Albert Hall on November 20.
OL,11,FThe celebrity line-up and royal
OL,12,Fattendees for the star-studded event
OL,13,Fwill be unveiled at a later date.
OL,15,FLast year, the Prince and Princess of
OL,16,FWales met Paddington, enjoyed a
OL,17,Fperformance from the new musical about
OL,18,Fthe marmalade-loving bear, and Kate
OL,19,Fshared a hug with the singer Jessie J,
OL,20,Fprompted by their shared experience of
OL,21,Fcancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
