OL,3,CTickets for 99th Royal Variety
OL,4,CPerformance go on sale this Friday
OL,6,FTo close the show, a cast of 400
OL,7,Fperformed a special medley of songs
OL,8,Ffrom Les Miserables to celebrate the
OL,9,Fmusical's 40th anniversary.
OL,11,FThe event is staged in aid of the
OL,12,FRoyal Variety Charity, of which the
OL,13,FKing is patron, and money raised helps
OL,14,Fpeople from the world of entertainment
OL,15,Fin need of care and assistance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
