OL,3,CTickets for 99th Royal Variety
OL,4,CPerformance go on sale this Friday
OL,6,FIn 2024, the organisation established
OL,7,Fa mental health sub-committee to help
OL,8,Findividuals experiencing anxiety,
OL,9,Fdepression, addiction and other mental
OL,10,Fhealth issues often exacerbated by
OL,11,Ffinancial instability and the
OL,12,Funpredictable nature of employment in
OL,13,Fthe entertainment industry.
OL,15,FThe charity also runs its own
OL,16,Fresidential care home, Brinsworth
OL,17,FHouse, affectionately known as the Old
OL,18,FPro's Paradise, in Twickenham, south-
OL,19,Fwest London, for retired artists and
OL,20,Fentertainers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
