OL,3,CTickets for 99th Royal Variety
OL,4,CPerformance go on sale this Friday
OL,6,FThe origins of the Royal Variety
OL,7,FPerformance date back to 1912, when
OL,8,FKing George V and Queen Mary agreed to
OL,9,Fattend a Royal Command Performance at
OL,10,Fthe Palace Theatre in London, in aid
OL,11,Fof the Variety Artistes' Benevolent
OL,12,FFund.
