OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772179261
OL,3,CTickets for 99th Royal Variety
OL,4,CPerformance go on sale this Friday
OL,6,FGiles Cooper, executive producer of
OL,7,Fthe show and chairman of the charity,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Royal Variety Charity is
OL,9,Fthrilled that the Royal Variety
OL,10,FPerformance will be returning to the
OL,11,Ficonic Royal Albert Hall this year
OL,12,Fafter our very successful, five star
OL,13,Freviewed show in 2025, attended by
OL,14,FTheir Royal Highnesses the Prince and
OL,15,FPrincess of Wales."
OL,17,FHe described the event as an "annual
OL,18,Fgreat British institution" which
OL,19,Fprovides "crucial fundraising" to
OL,20,Fsupport those in "our much-loved
OL,21,Fentertainment industry".
